<footer>
    <div class="footer-columns">
        <div class="footer-column">
            <h3 class="overskrift">FAQ</h3>
            <div class="faq">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4 class="question">What payment methods do we offer?</h4>
                    <p class="answer">We offer: VISA - Mastercard - MobilePay - Cash </p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4 class="question">How do I book an appointment?</h4>
                    <p class="answer">You can book an appointment by visiting the store, by insta, by the site or by calling the number: <br><br> + 45 60 18 16 63</p>
                </div>
                 <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4 class="question">How much does a tattoo cost?</h4>
                    <p class="answer">The price depends on the size. We have a starting fee of DKK 800. Contact us for more information.</p>
                </div>
                 <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4 class="question">Terms regarding advance payment & cancellation</h4>
                    <p class="answer">We charge a desosit of 25% of the booking value. The pre-paid deposit is not refounded in the event of cancellation if it happens 5 days before the appointment.</p>
                </div>
                 <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4 class="question">Preparation for tattoo session</h4>
                    <p class="answer">We encourage you to avoird alcohol the days before and after your session for the best healing process. In addition, get a good meal before you show up.</p>
                </div>
