                    <h4 class="question">How do I take care of my new tattoo?</h4>
                    <p class="answer">You will receive an introduktion to how to treat your new tattoo after your session. <br><br> In case you have any questions, you can read more here: <a class="link_aftercare" href="https://mst.dk/borger/sundhed-og-kemi/personlig-pleje/think-before-you-ink/efter-tatovering" target="_blank">After care</a> </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
